osc_a1_fine.name: osc_a1_fine
osc_a1_fine.description: Pitch can be fine-tuned between two half notes for Oscillator A1

osc_a1_invert.name: osc_a1_invert
osc_a1_invert.description: The Oscillator A1 Invert button inverts the Oscillator A1’s output (Boolean False=Off, True=On). This can be useful when creating PWM-like sound effects. For example, if you add two saw oscillators and invert one of them, the resulting waveform will be a pulse. You can then adjust the pulse width by changing the phase of one of the oscillators.

osc_a1_note.name: osc_a1_note
osc_a1_note.description: Tune the voices of Oscillator A1 to another specific note

osc_a1_octave.name: osc_a1_octave
osc_a1_octave.description: Tune the voices of Oscillator A1 to another specific octave

osc_a1_pan.name: osc_a1_pan
osc_a1_pan.description: Pans the output of Oscillator A1 to the left (-10) or right (10) channel.

osc_a1_phase_deg.name: osc_a1_phase_deg
osc_a1_phase_deg.description: This knob will change the starting point of Oscillator A1's waveform. It will only function when Retrigger is enabled.

osc_a1_retrigger.name: osc_a1_retrigger
osc_a1_retrigger.description: The Retrigger button can be used to force all of Oscillator A1's voices to start at the exact same location on the waveform every time a new note is played (Boolean False=Off, True=On). That location can be changed using the Phase knob. If Phase is set to 0, the voices will restart at the beginning of the waveform period. If it is set to 180 degrees, the voices will start halfway the period, while setting it to 360 degrees will make them start at the end of the waveform, which is equivalent to the beginning.

osc_a1_stereo.name: osc_a1_stereo
osc_a1_stereo.description: Sets the level of stereo separation between Oscillator A1's individual voices. If set to 0 it will generate a mono sound, if set to 10 the voices will be fully spread over the left and right channels. This only has effect if there are more than 1 voices.

osc_a1_volume.name: osc_a1_volume
osc_a1_volume.description: Sets the output volume of Oscillator A1

osc_a1_waveform.name: osc_a1_waveform
osc_a1_waveform.description: Type of Waveform for Oscillator A1
